          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Unlock Super Turbo -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Triangle, Right, Right, Circle, Left.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "Ripper Roo" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Right, Circle, Circle, Down, Up, Down, Right.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "Papu Papu" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Right, Down, Right, Circle, Left, Left, Down.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "Komodo Joe" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Down, Circle, Left, Left, Triangle, Right, Down.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "Ripper Roo" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Right, Circle, Circle, Down, Up, Down, Right.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "N Tropy" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Down, Left, Right, Up, Down, Right, Right.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "Penta Penguin" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Down, Right, Triangle, Down, Left, Triangle, Up.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock "Pinstripe" -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Goto the MAIN MENU and while holding L1+R1 enter the following: Left, Right, Triangle, Down, Right, Down.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
